  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deck Building Roguelike with a twist!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A silly little Deckbuilding card battler! Attack enemies, Gain Block, Get Cards/Relics, Remove Cards, and kill enemies! However, you can use your cards on more then yourself and enemies:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Cards on Status effects! </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Damage your Bleed to remove it or at least soften the blow! Heal your own Might to deal even more damage! Heal enemy Bleed to make them die faster! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/1fb5cd8f50c15b0bbe22fd33bf428917.poster.avif?t=1752517757\" width=390 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/1fb5cd8f50c15b0bbe22fd33bf428917.webm?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/1fb5cd8f50c15b0bbe22fd33bf428917.mp4?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Cards on Enemy intentions!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy enemies attacks, Offense is the best Defense! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/6f9cb39d5e7b6bc77ac3fcc13e2ae0dc.poster.avif?t=1752517757\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/6f9cb39d5e7b6bc77ac3fcc13e2ae0dc.webm?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/6f9cb39d5e7b6bc77ac3fcc13e2ae0dc.mp4?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Cards on Relics!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relic that lets you use 1 card on all enemies? Great for a deck around building up one super strike! A relic that lets you save a card for next turn? Could help with all sorts of combos. Find all sorts of \"Active\" relics! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/54d8ed3778cf53967d909aacbfbff761.poster.avif?t=1752517757\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/54d8ed3778cf53967d909aacbfbff761.webm?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/54d8ed3778cf53967d909aacbfbff761.mp4?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But most importantly...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combine Card Orbs via Keywords!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Cards on Cards! Cards will have all sorts of keywords that change how they work. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Potent cards will increase all Healing and status effects on a card! Useful for stacking all sorts of effects! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheap cards will cost less then they would otherwise!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Any more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These effects are great on their own, but even more powerful when put on another card!  Plan your deck around powerful combinations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original Card</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/e571560cfa463afd8053aaf81bf5b1f6.avif?t=1752517757\" width=260 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>After some Combining!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/780c1ccfc2c3f5a6fe02a9d2409e6fc5.avif?t=1752517757\" width=252 height=224 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Real Talk</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is made by 1 solo developer who just really likes card games who truly hopes you have a bit of fun playing this silly little game!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deck Building Roguelike with a twist!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A silly little Deckbuilding card battler! Attack enemies, Gain Block, Get Cards/Relics, Remove Cards, and kill enemies! However, you can use your cards on more then yourself and enemies:  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Cards on Status effects! </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Damage your Bleed to remove it or at least soften the blow! Heal your own Might to deal even more damage! Heal enemy Bleed to make them die faster! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/1fb5cd8f50c15b0bbe22fd33bf428917.poster.avif?t=1752517757\" width=390 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/1fb5cd8f50c15b0bbe22fd33bf428917.webm?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/1fb5cd8f50c15b0bbe22fd33bf428917.mp4?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Cards on Enemy intentions!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy enemies attacks, Offense is the best Defense! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/6f9cb39d5e7b6bc77ac3fcc13e2ae0dc.poster.avif?t=1752517757\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/6f9cb39d5e7b6bc77ac3fcc13e2ae0dc.webm?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/6f9cb39d5e7b6bc77ac3fcc13e2ae0dc.mp4?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use Cards on Relics!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A relic that lets you use 1 card on all enemies? Great for a deck around building up one super strike! A relic that lets you save a card for next turn? Could help with all sorts of combos. Find all sorts of \"Active\" relics! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/54d8ed3778cf53967d909aacbfbff761.poster.avif?t=1752517757\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/54d8ed3778cf53967d909aacbfbff761.webm?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/54d8ed3778cf53967d909aacbfbff761.mp4?t=1752517757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But most importantly...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combine Card Orbs via Keywords!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Cards on Cards! Cards will have all sorts of keywords that change how they work. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Potent cards will increase all Healing and status effects on a card! Useful for stacking all sorts of effects! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cheap cards will cost less then they would otherwise!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Any more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These effects are great on their own, but even more powerful when put on another card!  Plan your deck around powerful combinations. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original Card</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/e571560cfa463afd8053aaf81bf5b1f6.avif?t=1752517757\" width=260 height=126 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>After some Combining!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2317320/extras/780c1ccfc2c3f5a6fe02a9d2409e6fc5.avif?t=1752517757\" width=252 height=224 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Real Talk</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is made by 1 solo developer who just really likes card games who truly hopes you have a bit of fun playing this silly little game!</p>",
